review_blob: This is a very good seasonal. Like it the "porter" characteristics. This seasons was a bit more metalic in the mouth, but a little aging and it should be very good. Once it hits the 11% mark it should make for a very nice sipping beer!

This is a great porter. Anything made in Bob Marleys honor is cool. Had a nice body with a fruity aroma. Berry aroma would be about right. Like the new packaging with the Jamacian Colors. Support your local brew

This is a great and refreshing beer. Package is got a good design and it comes in a 500ml bottle so it is more bang for your buck. It is a bit on the lighter body style, but overall a good beer. Hope you enjoy
